OL,6,FJust 24 hours after the murder of
OL,7,Fthree young girls in a Southport dance
OL,8,Fstudio - the seaside town still
OL,9,Freeling from this appalling act,
OL,10,Fexploded into violence.
OL,12,FThe scenes that unfolded outside the
OL,13,Flocal mosque on the evening of 30 July
OL,14,Fwere fuelled by online rumour and
OL,15,Fdisinformation with lies spreading
OL,16,Fthat the perpetrator of the attack at
OL,17,Fthe Hart Space was Muslim or an
OL,18,Fillegal immigrant.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
