OL,4,Chatred directed towards us'
OL,6,FAn information vacuum allowed a false
OL,7,Fnarrative to develop that was picked
OL,8,Fup and amplified by far right sources.
OL,10,FHundreds targeted Southport Mosque
OL,11,Fand, before the evening was over, the
OL,12,Fworst violence the country had seen in
OL,13,Fa decade injured dozens of police
OL,14,Fofficers, damaged buildings and saw
OL,15,Fvehicles torched.
OL,17,FSpeaking one year on from the events
OL,18,Fof that night chairman of Southport
OL,19,FMosque Iman Ibrahim Hussain said that
OL,20,Fthey are still seeing an impact.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
