OL,4,Chatred directed towards us'
OL,6,F"Unfortunately we have reported to the
OL,7,Fpolice about six or seven incidents
OL,8,Fsince last year," he said.
OL,10,F"In the 30 years before, we had
OL,11,Freported reported three. We feel there
OL,12,Fis undercurrent of hatred directed
OL,13,Ftowards us. That's even though the
OL,14,Fworld now knows that this guy
OL,15,F(Rudakubana) had nothing to do with us.
OL,17,F"Southport has always been a nice
OL,18,Fquiet town and we go about our
OL,19,Fbusiness as normal.
