OL,4,Chatred directed towards us'
OL,6,F"The support that we've had from the
OL,7,Fcommunity since is heartwarming and
OL,8,Fincredible it shows the true colour of
OL,9,Fthe people of southport.
OL,11,F"Obviously there are a few people bent
OL,12,Fon causing trouble and creating
OL,13,Fhatred. Thankfully they are the
OL,14,Fminority. We are very happy with our
OL,15,Fdear dear community."
OL,17,FIn the days that followed, disorder
OL,18,Fspread across the country with scenes
OL,19,Fin places including Manchester,
OL,20,FLiverpool, Leeds and Newcastle.
