OL,6,FIn Piccadilly Gardens, in the centre
OL,7,Fof Manchester, shops were looted,
OL,8,Fbricks and bottles were thrown at
OL,9,Fpolice, and in one incident a lone
OL,10,Fblack man was set upon by a mob.
OL,12,F"Sydney", who asked ITV News to
OL,13,Fprotect her real identity, is part of
OL,14,Fthe Caribbean and African health
OL,15,Fnetwork in Manchester.
OL,17,F"Manchester has been my home for 22
OL,18,Fyears before the riot, I felt safe,
OL,19,Fbut after the riot, it made me feel
OL,20,Funsafe," she said.
