OL,6,F"I have family members around, I have
OL,7,Fchildren. Thinking that something
OL,8,Fsimilar could happen to us - it was
OL,9,Ffrightening."
OL,11,FIn the months that followed, hundreds
OL,12,Fwere arrested, charged and jailed with
OL,13,FPrime minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,14,Fpromising swift action for "far right
OL,15,Fthugs".
OL,17,FWhilst the Prime minister was happy to
OL,18,Fpoint the finger at those on the
OL,19,Fpolitical fringes others have said the
OL,20,Fsituation that followed the initial
OL,21,Fdisorder was less clear cut.
