OL,6,FThe Children's Commissioner suggested
OL,7,Fthat thrill-seeking and a lack of
OL,8,Ftrust in police were the driving
OL,9,Ffactors for many young people to get
OL,10,Finvolved - more than online
OL,11,Fmisinformation.
OL,13,FThe Institute for Public Policy
OL,14,Fresearch (IPPR) has suggested another
OL,15,Ffactor, with a decline in community
OL,16,Fspaces and local amenities in many
OL,17,Fareas.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
