OL,3,C'We feel there is an undercurrent of
OL,4,Chatred directed towards us'
OL,6,FDr Sacha Hilhorst from the IPPR said:
OL,7,F"The Southport riots were a wake-up
OL,8,Fcall ` a stark reminder of what can
OL,9,Fhappen when communities lose the
OL,10,Fplaces that once brought people
OL,11,Ftogether.
OL,13,F"In the absence of shared spaces,
OL,14,Fmisinformation and hate can fill the
OL,15,Fvoid, creating tinderbox conditions
OL,16,Ffor violence."
