OL,6,FA recent report released by the
OL,7,FPeople's Health Trust which surveyed
OL,8,Fmany of the affected areas laid bare
OL,9,Fthe lingering impact of the riots with
OL,10,Fmany residents reporting hyper
OL,11,Fvigilance, higher rates of anxiety,
OL,12,Fchronic stress and fear of accessing
OL,13,Fpublic spaces.
OL,15,FPeople's Health Trust CEO, John Hume
OL,16,Fsaid: "Last year's racist riots have
OL,17,Fleft a deep scar, especially in
OL,18,Fcommunities already facing inequality,
OL,19,Fdiscrimination, and disinvestment.
