OL,6,F"We need to address the root causes of
OL,7,Fthis violence which is both
OL,8,Fmisinformation across the media and
OL,9,Fsocial media and the deepening
OL,10,Fdissatisfaction resulting from decades
OL,11,Fof austerity, poor housing and cost of
OL,12,Fliving crises.
OL,14,F"Now is the time for meaningful
OL,15,Fcoordinated action from decision-
OL,16,Fmakers at a national and local level"
